Heading: How Jira Helps in Tracking

Content:

Dashboards: High-level visibility of progress.

Kanban/Scrum Boards: Visualize workflows.

Roadmaps: Monitor epic-level progress over time.

Reports: Burndown charts, velocity charts, and issue tracking.

Linked Issues: Easily navigate dependencies.




